label: ABCD Equivalence
rdfs_comment: Used to show the xpath(s) to the equivalent term(s) in the current version of the Access to Biological Collections Data (ABCD) schema.

label: Organized in Class
rdfs_comment: Used to organize properties within classes for easier human understanding.

label: Has Decision
rdfs_comment: Used to reference the formal decision that resulted in this version of the term.

label: Status
rdfs_comment: Used to indicate if the term is recommended for use or if it is only of historical significance.

label: Term List
rdfs_comment: An IRI-identified set of terms that is part of a vocabulary and that includes terms within the vocabulary that are grouped in a particular way, such as falling within a particular namespace.

label: Layer
rdfs_comment: Used to indicate the centrality of vocabulary terms.

label: Required
rdfs_comment: Indicates that a term is required to conform to a profile.

label: Repeatable
rdfs_comment: Indicates that the term may be repeated in a metadata record.

label: Use with IRI
rdfs_comment: Indicates that the term should have an IRI value.

label: A Decision
rdfs_comment: A decision made by the TDWG Executive Committee.

label: Management Category
rdfs_comment: Indicates that the term should be included in the Management category.

label: Attribution Category
rdfs_comment: Indicates that the term should be included in the Attribution category.

label: Content Coverage Category
rdfs_comment: Indicates that the term should be included in the Content Coverage category.

label: Taxonomic Coverage Category
rdfs_comment: Indicates that the term should be included in the Taxonomic Coverage category.

label: Resource Creation Category
rdfs_comment: Indicates that the term should be included in the Resource Creation category.

label: Related Resources Category
rdfs_comment: Indicates that the term should be included in the Related Resources category.

label: Service Access Point
rdfs_comment: A specific digital representation of a resource (e.g., a specific resolution, quality, or format).

label: Usage Scope
rdfs_comment: Indicates whether a term is part of Simple Darwin Core or extended Darwin Core
